class="block-intro-text"><p>The best handyman websites have a professional appearance, with easily accessible information about the types of services offered, locations served, and whether the company offers residential and/or commercial services. The home page should also include contact information and a link to testimonials from satisfied customers.</p><p>If you're looking to start a handyman business, you can use our <a
href="/">handyman AI website builder</a> to create a clean, professional website in just a few seconds.</p></div><div
