class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="fantastic-handyman" class="entry-website-title">Fantastic Handyman</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-fantastic-handyman-desktop-3840x4302-20240528.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-fantastic-handyman-desktop-3840x4302-20240528.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-fantastic-handyman-desktop-3840x4302-20240528.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Fantastic Handyman"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://www.fantastichandyman.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://www.fantastichandyman.co.uk/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>London, U.K.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Fantastic Handyman provides residential handyman services in and around London, from small odd jobs to complete property refurbishments. As part of the Fantastic Services group, the website offers comprehensive service information, with detailed pricing, a full list of services, contact numbers, and a handy online booking feature.</p><p>Unlike many competitors, Fantastic Handyman includes a blog page, a rewards club, and detailed information about the team and founders. We appreciated that the website provided detailed pricing for regular hours, weekends, and after-hours.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The website includes pricing for hourly rates, after-hours, and weekends. Customers can book a service online. WAVE picked up very few contrast errors.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The Trustpilot reviews should be more prominent. The website does not have an FAQ section.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-fantastic-handyman-desktop-3840x4302-20240528.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-fantastic-handyman-desktop-3840x4302-20240528.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website looks good on larger screens and loads quickly. Navigation is straightforward, and the layout utilizes the available screen space effectively to display the text and high-quality images of the handyman team. The desktop website scores 98/100 for performance on Google's PageSpeed Insights test, confirming the fast response times seen in our real-world tests.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-fantasic-handyman-mobile-824x13558-20240528.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-fantasic-handyman-mobile-824x13558-20240528.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The Fantastic Handyman website performs well on mobile, with fast loading times, easy navigation, and a good balance of large text and images on the page. The addition of the floating call button is a nice feature for quick bookings. The mobile website performed well in our tests and scored 98/100 for performance on PageSpeed Insights.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="hire-a-hubby" class="entry-website-title">Hire a Hubby</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hire-a-hubby-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hire-a-hubby-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hire-a-hubby-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Hire a Hubby"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://hireahubby.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://hireahubby.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Milton Keynes, Buckinghamshire, U.K.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Hire a Hubby is a property maintenance company offering commercial and domestic handyman services across the U.K. The website places a lot of focus on trust and reliability, with an extensive reviews page, case studies, and a "why choose us" section.</p><p>The company's toll-free number is prominently displayed on each page and there is an option to request a free quote. At first glance, the website seems to be missing pertinent information, but much of the content, including a blog page, About page, gift vouchers, and articles can only be found from links hidden at the bottom of the page.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>Visitors can request a free quote. The website promises 100% workmanship guaranteed. All "Hubbies" are police checked and carry photo ID.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>Certain content like the blog page can only be found through links at the bottom of the page. WAVE also picked up a number of contrast errors on the site.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hire-a-hubby-20240522-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hire-a-hubby-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website looks good on larger screens, but has slow loading times, especially when navigating to different pages on the site. While most information is easily accessible from the navigation menu, the top menu quickly disappears as you scroll down the page, replaced by a back-to-top button.</p><p>The desktop website scored 59/100 for performance on Google's PageSpeed Insights test, verifying the slow loading times seen in real-world tests.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hire-a-hubby-mobile-824x7704-20240528.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hire-a-hubby-mobile-824x7704-20240528.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>Hire a Hubby's mobile website adapts well to smaller screens but also has slow loading times. The images are clear and the text is large and easy to read. As with the desktop site, a back-to-top button assists when scrolling through the content. The mobile website scored 56/100 for performance on Google's PageSpeed Insights test, matching the slow speed found in real-world tests.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="chris-jenson-handyman" class="entry-website-title">Chris Jenson Handyman</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-chris-jenson-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-chris-jenson-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-chris-jenson-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Chris Jenson Handyman"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://www.chrisjensonhandymanbexley.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://www.chrisjensonhandymanbexley.com/
</a></p><p
