height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Andy OnCall"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://andyoncall.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://andyoncall.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Chattanooga, Tennessee, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Andy OnCall is a domestic handyman repair service company operating in Chattanooga, Tennessee. The Andy OnCall website isn't the easiest to navigate with the testimonials nested under the "About Us" section and a dedicated menu for "Craftmen" not intended for clients.</p><p>That said, the home page has a prominent "Free Quote" and "Call" button to get in touch. Pricing is also mentioned and the site includes a news page, with handy tips and information about home repairs. We felt that site would benefit from an FAQ section and a portfolio page of completed projects.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>Visitors can easily request a free estimate. The website includes a news/blog page.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The testimonials page is difficult to find. The website does not mention liability insurance. WAVE also picked up a few accessibility errors. There is no FAQ section or portfolio page.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-andy-on-call-20240522-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-andy-on-call-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website is visually appealing, with a good mix of images and text on each page. The sticky top menu provides easy navigation assisted by a back-to-top button. The desktop website scored 97/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test confirming the fast loading times experienced in our real-world tests.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-andy-on-call-20240522-mobile.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
