class="entry-text"><p>The mobile website is perfectly adapted for smaller screens, spacing out the large color images and text blocks to not seem overwhelming. More scrolling is required, but the floating menu and back-to-top buttons provide navigational assistance. The mobile site received good scores for SEO, best practices, and accessibility on Google's PageSpeed Insights test but scored 67/100 for performance.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
