<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Washtenaw County, Michigan, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Apex Handyman Services is a general contractor offering a wide range of handyman services in Washtenaw County, Michigan. The website features a simple one-page layout, with a top menu that directs readers to various sections, including the services offered, customer testimonials, and a small photo gallery showcasing completed projects.</p><p>While the site looks professional, it's missing a few key features like an FAQ section and pricing information. Additionally, clicking on the "About Us" section brings up a small popup, with text that is difficult to read.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site has a comprehensive list of big and small projects the team can help with. The "Community" page includes links to companies that have used the service.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site does not mention pricing or liability insurance. WAVE picked up contrast errors on every page.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-apex-handyman-services-20240522-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
