alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>On desktop devices, the website background images and hero banner provide visual appeal, while the text is neatly encased in blocks for easy reading. The density of the single-page setup means slower page loading times, but we felt they were within acceptable limits. The desktop site scored 54/100 for performance on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-apex-handyman-services-20240526-mobile.webp"
