</span>
<span>Hamilton, Montana, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Zach of All Trades is a handyman and renovation service company based in Hamilton, Montana. The website offers easy access to pertinent information including operating hours, a project gallery, a list of services, Google reviews, and details about the four-step process for getting a job done.</p><p>A nice feature of the site is the before and after photo slider, where clients can see the transformations of previous projects. The site also includes "Free Estimate" and "Request a Project" links. That said, we felt the site would benefit from an FAQ section and pricing information.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
